    }
  },
  "notes": [
    "Form implements IBaseSearch interface for main form integration",
    "Grid supports multi-row selection (Extended SelectType)",
    "Search requires at least one criteria to prevent long-running queries",
    "Expandable combos toggle between Full and Filtered modes via header click",
    "Location type combos have mutual exclusivity - both cannot be 'Boat' simultaneously",
    "Freight-related controls/columns conditionally shown based on license",
    "Grid settings (column widths, sorting) persist per user",
    "Void events displayed with gray strikethrough formatting",
